why would you want to create a remote pository rather than keep all your work local?
so you can share your work with others
Describe the differences between forks, clones, and branches. When would you use one instead of another?
fork: when you copy a reposiotry from a repository in github
clone:when you copy a repository to local from your repository on github
branches: when you want to have different commits for your repository either on github or local
